Huawei’s Mate20 Pro is a trailblazer in smartphone technology, and as such, it has won numerous awards, including Product of the Year in the Smartphone Category for 2019 It has been recognised for its innovative identity and groundbreaking technologies that bring consumers the ultimate user experience. The device was explicitly commended for its powerful performance, outstanding camera system, long battery life, innovative charging solutions, and striking design. In celebration of the success of the smartphone in South Africa, Huawei has launched its March promotion, through which customers will get the Huawei Watch GT, valued at R5,499, free with their purchase of the Huawei Mate20 Pro. The high-end Watch GT features a slim, lightweight design while offering high-end wearable specifications and several exercise-related software features. Huawei’s Watch GT is water resistant up to 50m and includes a variety of sensors which can measure heart rate, movement, atmospheric pressure, and sleep patterns. It also boasts a battery life of up to two weeks and is available in two designs – Sport and Classic. Purchase your device in store today and visit www.huaweipromo.co.za to claim your Huawei Watch GT. The promotion ends on 31 March 2019, and Ts and Cs apply. <img class="size-full wp-image-297968 aligncenter" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Mate-20-Pro-Watch-GT.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Mate-20-Pro-Watch-GT.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Mate-20-Pro-Watch-GT-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Mate-20-Pro-Watch-GT-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" />